{
  "stem": "6878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I put them on his desk, and he counted half the money and then pushes up to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's for you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I pushed myself-- I pulled myself back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was never a gonif in my life, and all of a sudden, he forced me with that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I argued with him until he started to shout at me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, take the money, or get the hell out of it all together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I took the money, I walked out, and that was the start of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Being in the stores, we used to have sometimes 30 German prisoners who were working for me because there used to come in a lot of goods.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to lay them on the shelves, and I used to ask in the office to give me some labor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to send some.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to get goods and then sell them stuff, sometimes unused suits and this and that and everything-- everything from Germany-- carpets, furniture, everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't allowed to be rough to them, I was told, but occasionally I used to give a smack one, but occasionally.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them are-- uh, I tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ordinary army from the Germans, they even didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only the SS, but an ordinary soldier, he didn't even know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even if he knew, he wouldn't say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what could I do to them?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't do anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, I hate them like poison, but in my heart, but I couldn't show that I-- with I'm hatred to them with hate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started to have money unbelievable because of stealing goods from the stores and selling them and sharing with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
